t: Let All Things Praise the Lord
Praise*pn the Lord!*s Praise*ln God in His sanctuary; Praise*ld Him in His mighty firmament!
Praise*ln Him for His mighty acts; Praise*ld Him according to His excellent greatness!
Praise*ln Him with the sound of the trumpet; Praise*ld Him with the lute and harp!
Praise*ld Him with the timbrel and dance; Praise*ld Him with stringed instruments and flutes!
Praise*ld Him with loud cymbals; Praise*ld Him with clashing cymbals!
Let*ln everything that has breath praise the Lord.*s Praise*ln the Lord!*s
